# Enforce LF line endings regardless of the committing machine's OS/git
# config. Matters concretely for this repo: .claude/hooks/session-start.sh
# has a bash shebang — a CRLF-corrupted shebang line fails to execute on
# Linux (both this sandbox and EAS Build's Linux build servers), even
# though it'd look fine and run fine on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.sh text eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ttf binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
